{
  "texts": [
    "BERT is especially adept at comprehending the context of words in a phrase since it was trained on a large text sample.",
    "A few activities that BERT is helpful for are sentiment analysis, named entity identification, and question-answering.",
    "Most information in the pharmaceutical industry is based on the structures of small molecules and comparatively larger molecules (receptors, amino acids, antibodies, etc.).",
    "The representation of these structures may take the form of strings or other sequences.",
    "For instance, DeepMind (an Alphabet-owned company) used a transformer known as AlphaFold2 to increase our knowledge of proteins."
  ]
}